\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 - Before the modern age, so much misunderstanding.\line Talking just movement of air, like choking on a rope. It has no meaning on its own (just natter). No meaning to the wheezing/choking at the dinnertable/hanging. I worked this out. Wish I had worked it out earlier.}
