\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 - Use the thread as a line - hold one end in mouth, other end tied to finger. Spool it out.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 - When the wind is low, clear weather (can change it if you need) - colder is better, less stuff in the air.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 - Harder to get to dead, so should do at night.}
